Body:
with expected_protocol(ik.thorlabs.TC200, ['stat?', 'stat?', 'stat?',
    'unit=c', 'unit=f', 'unit=k'], ['stat?', '44 > stat?', '54 > stat?',
    '0 >  unit=c', '> unit=f', '> unit=k', '> '], sep='\r') as tc:
    assert str(tc.degrees).split(' ')[1] == 'K'
    assert str(tc.degrees).split(' ')[1] == 'degC'
    assert tc.degrees == u.degF
    tc.degrees = u.degC
    tc.degrees = u.degF
    tc.degrees = u.degK
